  "title": "【夜读】善于提供情绪价值，也是一种了不起的能力",
  "content": "<div class=\"rich_media_content js_underline_content defaultNoSetting\" id=\"js_content\">\n <p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n  <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-backh=\"425\" data-backw=\"300\" data-cropselx1=\"11\" data-cropselx2=\"290\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"425\" data-imgfileid=\"519473820\" data-ratio=\"1.4175925925925925\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"/static/res/logo/https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/xrFYciaHL08AiawVgWGG1QAVTcU1f5TVLtvicvhYxyqAqricwHGdHo9c4LBbFep949NpzveEjtwEibU2rtDxLYjhLeg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto !important;\"/>\n </p>\n <section>\n  <mp-common-mpaudio author=\"人民日报\" class=\"js_editor_audio res_iframe js_uneditable custom_select_card\" cover=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/xrFYciaHL08AiawVgWGG1QAVTcU1f5TVLttq6CltQVCReBpNuMjHS1QPtGcJtgGW9ZicBibmAHQJOictj3CGKMrbOwQ/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-pluginname=\"insertaudio\" data-topic_id=\"\" data-topic_name=\"\" data-trans_state=\"1\" data-verify_state=\"3\" high_size=\"2613.74\" isaac2=\"1\" low_size=\"602.43\" name=\"善于提供情绪价值，也是一种了不起的能力\" play_length=\"334000\" source_size=\"602.4\" src=\"/cgi-bin/readtemplate?t=tmpl/audio_tmpl&amp;name=%E5%96%84%E4%BA%8E%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E6%83%85%E7%BB%AA%E4%BB%B7%E5%80%BC%EF%BC%8C%E4%B9%9F%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E7%A7%8D%E4%BA%86%E4%B8%8D%E8%B5%B7%E7%9A%84%E8%83%BD%E5%8A%9B&amp;play_length=5%E5%88%86%E9%92%9F\" voice_encode_fileid=\"MjM5MjAxNDM4MF8yNjY2OTU3NTQ1\">\n  </mp-common-mpaudio>\n </section>\n <p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n  <span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">\n  </span>\n </p>\n <section style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">\n  <section style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin-top: 10px;\">\n   <section style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: auto;align-self: stretch;flex: 0 0 auto;background-color: rgb(93, 142, 255);min-width: 5%;height: auto;padding-left: 13px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-top: 5px;\">\n     <section style=\"text-align: justify;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 18px;\">\n      <p style=\"\">\n       <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n        <strong>\n         生活有多美好，取决于你对它有多热爱\n        </strong>\n       </span>\n      </p>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: 23px;align-self: stretch;flex: 0 0 auto;background-color: rgb(93, 142, 255);overflow: hidden;height: auto;\">\n    <section style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n     <p style=\"\">\n      <br/>\n     </p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: auto;min-width: 5%;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;align-self: stretch;overflow: hidden;padding-right: 7px;padding-left: 22px;margin-left: -20px;\">\n    <section style=\"transform: rotateZ(338deg);\">\n     <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: -10px;margin-bottom: -3px;transform: translate3d(-6px, 0px, 0px);\">\n      <section style=\"display: inline-block;width: 10px;height: 49px;vertical-align: top;overflow: hidden;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-shadow: rgb(255, 255, 255) -7px 0px 0px 0px;\">\n       <svg style=\"float:left;line-height:0;width:0;vertical-align:top;\" viewbox=\"0 0 1 1\">\n       </svg>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin-bottom: 10px;\">\n   <section style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: auto;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 0%;height: auto;\">\n    <section style=\"\">\n     <section style=\"display: inline-block;width: 0px;height: 0px;vertical-align: top;overflow: hidden;border-style: solid;border-width: 6px;border-color: rgb(57, 107, 223) rgb(57, 107, 223) rgba(255, 255, 255, 0) rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);\">\n      <section style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n       <p style=\"\">\n        <br/>\n       </p>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: auto;align-self: flex-start;flex: 100 100 0%;background-color: rgba(93, 142, 255, 0.11);height: auto;padding: 27px;\">\n    <section style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n     <p style=\"\">\n      <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n       网上有个热门问答：“什么是情绪价值？”\n      </span>\n     </p>\n     <p style=\"\">\n      <br/>\n     </p>\n     <p style=\"\">\n      <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n       一个高赞的回答是：她做饭忘了放盐，他打趣说吃淡一点好，低盐饮食健康；\n       <span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">\n        他出差带回来一件偏大的纪念衫，她笑着说挺好，宽松更百搭\n       </span>\n       ……总之，不论他们做什么，在彼此的眼里，都有可取之处。\n      </span>\n     </p>\n     <p style=\"\">\n      <br/>\n     </p>\n     <p style=\"\">\n      <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n       生活时有考验，但这并不意味着我们就要把自己活成一个紧绷的人。很多时候，温柔才是坚强的底色。\n      </span>\n     </p>\n     <p style=\"\">\n      <br/>\n     </p>\n     <p style=\"\">\n      <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n       当我们的心变得温柔，我们才有能力去拥抱世界。常常秉持着温柔和善意与这个世界相处，我们才能感知到人间的美好、人生的可贵。\n      </span>\n     </p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n </section>\n <p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n  <br/>\n </p>\n <section style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">\n  <section style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin-top: 10px;\">\n   <section style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: auto;align-self: stretch;flex: 0 0 auto;background-color: rgb(93, 142, 255);min-width: 5%;height: auto;padding-left: 13px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-top: 5px;\">\n     <section style=\"text-align: justify;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 18px;\">\n      <p style=\"\">\n       <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n        <strong>\n         善于提供情绪价值的人，内心都很温暖\n        </strong>\n       </span>\n      </p>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: auto;min-width: 5%;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;align-self: stretch;overflow: hidden;padding-right: 7px;padding-left: 22px;margin-left: -20px;\">\n    <section style=\"transform: rotateZ(338deg);\">\n     <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: -10px;margin-bottom: -3px;transform: translate3d(-6px, 0px, 0px);\">\n      <section style=\"display: inline-block;width: 10px;height: 49px;vertical-align: top;overflow: hidden;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-shadow: rgb(255, 255, 255) -7px 0px 0px 0px;\">\n       <svg style=\"float:left;line-height:0;width:0;vertical-align:top;\" viewbox=\"0 0 1 1\">\n       </svg>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin-bottom: 10px;\">\n   <section style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: auto;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 0%;height: auto;\">\n    <section style=\"\">\n     <section style=\"display: inline-block;width: 0px;height: 0px;vertical-align: top;overflow: hidden;border-style: solid;border-width: 6px;border-color: rgb(57, 107, 223) rgb(57, 107, 223) rgba(255, 255, 255, 0) rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);\">\n      <section style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n       <p style=\"\">\n        <br/>\n       </p>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: auto;align-self: flex-start;flex: 100 100 0%;background-color: rgba(93, 142, 255, 0.11);height: auto;padding: 27px;\">\n    <section style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n     <p>\n      <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n       <span style=\"text-indent: 2em;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">\n        人与人的互动，离不开情绪的流动。同那些能够照顾彼此情绪的朋友在一起，会获得一种无声的滋润；而与那些总是抱怨、负能量满满的人在一起，心情也会变得很差。\n       </span>\n      </span>\n     </p>\n     <section style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">\n      <br/>\n     </section>\n     <section style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">\n      <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n       那些总能为别人提供情绪价值的人，一定是内心非常温暖的人。聊天时的一个点头，交流时的一句赞美，难过时的一个拥抱，这些细微处的情感表达，总是能在人与人之间传递温暖。\n      </span>\n     </section>\n     <p>\n      <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n       <br/>\n      </span>\n     </p>\n     <p>\n      <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n       因为有爱，所以善待。当一颗心得到另一颗心的滋养，才能彼此之间相处不累、久处不厌。这世界上的爱，正是由人与人之间一点一滴的温柔组成的。\n      </span>\n     </p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n </section>\n <p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n  <br/>\n </p>\n <section style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">\n  <section style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin-top: 10px;\">\n   <section style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: auto;align-self: stretch;flex: 0 0 auto;background-color: rgb(93, 142, 255);min-width: 5%;height: auto;padding-left: 13px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-top: 5px;\">\n     <section style=\"text-align: justify;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 18px;\">\n      <p style=\"\">\n       <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n        <strong>\n         善于提供情绪价值，是一种了不起的能力\n        </strong>\n       </span>\n      </p>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: 23px;align-self: stretch;flex: 0 0 auto;background-color: rgb(93, 142, 255);overflow: hidden;height: auto;\">\n    <section style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n     <p style=\"\">\n      <br/>\n     </p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: auto;min-width: 5%;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;align-self: stretch;overflow: hidden;padding-right: 7px;padding-left: 22px;margin-left: -20px;\">\n    <section style=\"transform: rotateZ(338deg);\">\n     <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: -10px;margin-bottom: -3px;transform: translate3d(-6px, 0px, 0px);\">\n      <section style=\"display: inline-block;width: 10px;height: 49px;vertical-align: top;overflow: hidden;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-shadow: rgb(255, 255, 255) -7px 0px 0px 0px;\">\n       <svg style=\"float:left;line-height:0;width:0;vertical-align:top;\" viewbox=\"0 0 1 1\">\n       </svg>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin-bottom: 10px;\">\n   <section style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: auto;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 0%;height: auto;\">\n    <section style=\"\">\n     <section style=\"display: inline-block;width: 0px;height: 0px;vertical-align: top;overflow: hidden;border-style: solid;border-width: 6px;border-color: rgb(57, 107, 223) rgb(57, 107, 223) rgba(255, 255, 255, 0) rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);\">\n      <section style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n       <p style=\"\">\n        <br/>\n       </p>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: auto;align-self: flex-start;flex: 100 100 0%;background-color: rgba(93, 142, 255, 0.11);height: auto;padding: 27px;\">\n    <section style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n     <p style=\"\">\n      <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n       善于提供情绪价值，并不意味着迁就讨好，而是一种发自内心的真诚和善良。善于提供情绪价值，也绝对不是委屈自己，而是在照顾好自己心情的基础上，给他人提供帮助。\n      </span>\n     </p>\n     <p style=\"\">\n      <br/>\n     </p>\n     <p style=\"\">\n      <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n       那些善于提供情绪价值的人，不仅能治愈他人，也能滋养自身。想要成为一个善于提供情绪价值的人，不妨从这三点做起：\n      </span>\n     </p>\n     <p style=\"\">\n      <br/>\n     </p>\n     <p style=\"\">\n      <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n       <strong>\n        一是耐心倾听，拥有情绪共鸣的能力。\n       </strong>\n       很多时候，懂得倾听比能说会道更有力量。它是心与心的共振，能让人际交往间的纽带更紧密。以心换心，方得人心。\n      </span>\n     </p>\n     <p style=\"\">\n      <br/>\n     </p>\n     <p style=\"\">\n      <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n       <strong>\n        二是心怀感恩，降低负面情绪的影响。\n       </strong>\n       提供情绪价值的前提是，自己成为一个情绪稳定的人。遇到负面情绪，一味地批评、抱怨只会让人越陷越深。当一个人更多地看到生活中的温暖，他就对生活多了一份理解，对他人多了一份包容，自会降低负面情绪的影响。\n      </span>\n     </p>\n     <p style=\"\">\n      <br/>\n     </p>\n     <p style=\"\">\n      <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n       <strong>\n        三是懂得欣赏，提升情绪感知的能量。\n       </strong>\n       那些懂得欣赏的人，能敏锐感知他人的情绪，总是能看到他人的闪光点，并发自内心地赞美。你给予的每一次掌声，或许在未来的某个时刻，会以意想不到的方式回馈于你。抛开偏见，不断提升情绪感知能力，才能让生命更加丰盈开阔。\n      </span>\n     </p>\n     <p style=\"\">\n      <br/>\n     </p>\n     <p style=\"\">\n      <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n       愿我们都能成为一个善良的人，既有能力照料好自己的情绪，还能为他人送去温暖、拂去尘埃。\n      </span>\n     </p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n </section>\n <p>\n  <br/>\n </p>\n <hr style=\"border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);\"/>\n <p style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'>\n  <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;\">\n   来源：人民日报夜读综合洞见等 | 主播：赵文龙\n  </span>\n </p>\n <h1 style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\">\n   <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\">\n    本期编辑：石磊，实习生：甘雨欣\n   </span>\n  </p>\n </h1>\n <h1 style='-webkit-tap-hig